---
// NewsletterSubscription.astro
// Anillo de suscripción: Obsidian -> Web -> Substack -> Blogger
---
<div class="newsletter-module glass-panel">
  <div class="terminal-header">
    <div class="terminal-dots">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </div>
    <span class="terminal-title">SUBSCRIPCIÓN_PROTOCOLO_ISAN.exe</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="newsletter-content">
    <h3>Suscripción a la Mediateca ISAN</h3>
    <p>Únete a la red de nutrición intelectual. Recibe notificaciones de nuevos ensayos, transmisiones del Ágora y publicaciones cruzadas con nuestro Substack (@isanatelier) y Google Blogger.</p>
    
    <form class="subscription-form" action="https://isanatelier.substack.com/subscribe" method="get" target="_blank">
      <div class="input-wrapper">
        <span class="prompt">></span>
        <input type="email" placeholder="ingresar_correo_electronico..." required class="email-input" />
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Ejecutar Conexión</button>
    </form>
    
    <div class="platform-links">
      <div class="link-item">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        <a href="https://isanatelier.substack.com" target="_blank">Substack</a>
      </div>
      <div class="link-item">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        <a href="https://www.isan-atelier.art" target="_blank">Google Blogger</a>
      </div>
      <div class="link-item">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        <a href="/grafo">Grafo Obsidian</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.newsletter-module {
  padding: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin: 4rem 0;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
}

.terminal-header {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
}

.terminal-dots {
  display: flex;
  gap: 6px;
}

.terminal-dots span {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
}

.terminal-title {
  font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.newsletter-content {
  padding: 2.5rem;
  text-align: center;
}

h3 {
  margin-top: 0;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  color: white;
}

p {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 1rem auto 2rem;
}

.subscription-form {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.input-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 400px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 0 1rem;
  transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
}

.input-wrapper:focus-within {
  border-color: var(--color-digital-cyan);
}

.prompt {
  color: var(--color-digital-cyan);
  font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-right: 0.5rem;
}

.email-input {
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  color: white;
  padding: 1rem 0;
  width: 100%;
  font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  outline: none;
}

.submit-btn {
  padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
  background: white;
  color: black;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 30px;
  font-weight: 700;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
}

.submit-btn:hover {
  background: var(--color-neural-red);
  color: white;
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--color-neural-red-glow);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.platform-links {
  margin-top: 3rem;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 2rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.link-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.status-dot {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  background: var(--color-digital-cyan);
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--color-digital-cyan);
}

.platform-links a {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}

.platform-links a:hover {
  color: white;
}
</style>
